GET
/projects
returns a list of all projects

/projects/:projectId
returns the project with the specified ID

/projects/:projectId/payments
returns a list of all payments within this project

/projects/:projectId/payments/:paymentId
returns the payment with the specified ID

/projects/:projectId/log
returns a list of all logEntries within this project

/projects/:projectId/log/:logEntryId
returns the logEntry with the specified ID

POST
/projects
creates a new project

/projects/:projectId/payments
creates a new payment for the project with the specified projectId

/projects/:projectId/log
creates a new logEntry for the project with the specified projectId

PUT
/projects/:projectId
updates the project with the specified projectId

DELETE
/projects/:projectId
deletes the project with the specified projectId

/projects/:projectId/payments/:paymentId
deletes the payment with the specified paymentId

/projects/:projectId/log/:logEntryId
deletes the logEntry with the specified logEntryId